message.body: Hello I'm at the zoo! How's life?
Hey...what zoo? You're lucky! I was just listening to a dozen voicemail messages from my drunk, depressed sister. But, on the upside, I leave in 4hrs to
drive to Vegas for the weekend. What's your favorite animal(s)?
Ooh! The Pittsburgh zoo, I'm visiting a friend. Sorry about your sister! Where are you driving from?
I think I like giraffes or mooses most :) you?
Driving from Tucson, AZ. Just visiting here. I live in Los Angeles. I dunno...giraffes definitely rank high on the list...
Never been to Pittsburgh. Been to Philly. Used to live in NYC.
Oh cool, I went to USC for college. I live in Delaware now.
I've heard that Delaware is beautiful! How do you like it? What did you major in?
Ok I don't know if my last message sent, that was weird. I majored in linguistics and math which is how I heard about this study! DE is ok, love the beaches anyway.
